      <title>据报道美国盟友不受限制，ASML 股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/asml-shares-jump-on-report-us-allies-exempt-from-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社报道，拜登政府计划将日本、荷兰和韩国的芯片设备制造商从即将出台的出口限制中豁免，此后 ASML 和东京电子引领全球半导体股上涨。彭博社的 Tom Mackenzie 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/asml-shares-jump-on-report-us-allies-exempt-from-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 07:55:29 GMT</pubDate>
